{"tid":893942,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"愛貓人士氣炸了《異塵餘生76》遊戲中玩家如果肚子餓可以吃貓，但不能收養？","createTime":"2018-11-08T04:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T06:39:40.000Z","uid":212399,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"68449405c21b5965a9c74f25221918d41e01271d","tid":893942,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:29:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/M9FGaan35s0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FM9FGaan35s0&d=AM57Ty9dh6zc9ptDLz4hr49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=81c88921\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/M9FGaan35s0</a><br />\n倍受玩家期待的Bethesda人氣系列新作《異塵餘生76》（Fallout 76），預計將於11月14日正式在PS4、Xbox One、PC平台發售，遊戲設定於核戰爭摧毀地球25年後，玩家必須在廢墟中覓食以維持生命，甚至連貓都可以吃，不過很抱歉，不能收養&mdash;&mdash;這設定讓貓奴氣炸了，揚言拒玩。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲設定在2102年的美國西維吉尼亞州，核戰爭摧毀地球25年後。除了其他玩家以外（所有的倖存人類皆由真實玩家扮演，遊戲不包含任何人類型態的非玩家角色），還有眾多突變怪物，如西維吉尼亞州民間傳說的天蛾人（Mothman）和弗拉特伍茲怪物（Flatwoods monster）。<br />\n<br />\n有細心玩家在《異塵餘生76》的NoClip的文件夾中發現了這個隱藏的設定&mdash;&mdash;可以吃貓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2018/16/97/q5iUpqGZl5_WsKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2018%2F16%2F97%2Fq5iUpqGZl5_WsKU.jpg&h=98634a17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然而Bethesda曾表示雖然遊戲中有各式各樣的生物，但玩家並不能收養，也就是在《異塵餘生76》中，貓咪僅僅是做為一種食材的存在。這讓愛貓人士氣到冒煙，表示人類和貓的關係不該僅止於此，對於這樣的設定表達強烈反彈，揚言拒玩這款遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n《異塵餘生76》正式版要等到11月14日發售，不知道是否會修改掉這個設定。"},{"pid":"3f1c5041bd6089ee9d48b9e31cf0c31b7d99651d","tid":893942,"uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353165e1f851cc0d02595dea2a26a5c5c20092d2","tid":893942,"uid":154505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:34:48.000Z","msg":"postal cat silencer想要HD<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c492179c0912904683565aa796ce0516ca10033","tid":893942,"uid":99607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:45:48.000Z","msg":"War never changes"},{"pid":"1f549d01ce169a21968225563e6d16f8ef0ad78a","tid":893942,"uid":165361,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:48:44.000Z","msg":"世界未日.. 食貓好合理"},{"pid":"61780381e0957fb6623ff8a3f79bdc5ae374ee83","tid":893942,"uid":55571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:14:58.000Z","msg":"人都食得啦<br />\n係咪要養埋奴"},{"pid":"c5df92f2e7a0a593f00df867d73426736d71f2eb","tid":893942,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:19:45.000Z","msg":"據說冇npc 可以點玩"},{"pid":"7840e2905b13a07f940cfab8b556d4d744786731","tid":893942,"uid":155019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:22:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔玩了"},{"pid":"7a6689d5306c3fb47f22bb2061284a394200c68f","tid":893942,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:32:31.000Z","msg":"鬼佬唔食貓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905cbb104d5c618c647ed900c12330521c6e6b6a","tid":893942,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a6689d5306c3fb47f22bb2061284a394200c68f","tid":893942,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:32:31.000Z","msg":"鬼佬唔食貓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:47:13.000Z","msg":"有得選就話<br />\n無得選唔通死都唔食"},{"pid":"44648fa7c24d7925615a9eab8b0d299e566ca5d1","tid":893942,"uid":144064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:01:45.000Z","msg":"都食左咁多集狗肉，終於可以轉下口味"},{"pid":"24fd89c545e389723652568b9539a96d578a3c7a","tid":893942,"uid":81308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:12:07.000Z","msg":"Dogmeat就拍擋<br />\n貓就食糧<br />\n愛貓人士玻璃心爆炸"},{"pid":"5a7eb715cb013225c237dfb5de4b